snippet.title: Pathfinder: Kingmaker - Varnhold's Lot DLC Trailer
snippet.description: Fearless conquerors of The Stolen Lands can now enjoy a complete self-contained side story that will test their resolve, stretch their leadership abilities and reveal truths, all from a previous companions point of view!
